law.history: Repealed 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 79, sec. 35, effective June 17, 1954. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 93, sec. 9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Income from trust for benefit of divorced or separated wife, when to be included in gross income of wife; purpose to treat alimony payments as under Federal law.
